<P>Cardinall <HI>Bellarmine</HI> thinks as Saint <HI>Hierom,</HI>
that there are but nine <HI>Homilies</HI> of Saint <HI>Basils,</HI>
the other two he supposes to bee <HI>Gregory Nys|sens:</HI>
and so this great Light went out, whose
