<P>These are the fruits of this Fathers labour,
he who desires to know which are truely Saint
<HI>Augustines,</HI> and which are suspected for adulte|rine,
let him read Cardinall <HI>Bellarmines</HI> obser|vations
<HI>de scriptoribus Ecclesiasti<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 letter">is,</HI> in the life of
Saint <HI>Augustine;</HI> but these doe shew what a
painfull labourer he was in the Vineyard of the
